responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "CA454B444CCB18B65D8CBD9B432C8838", "I should kill you! No, no. I am sorry. Fendris was corrupted. Clearly. Why would he help the bandits? Why? We should have stayed in Sanctus. There is no future in this poisoned world. Leave me be.")
